<lb n="5"/>varddhanulaina tribhuvanacakravarttiśrīkulōttuṁgacōḍadēvara pravarddhamānavi
<lb n="6" break="no"/>jayarājyasaṁvatsa 38 gu śrāhi dina 350 <unclear>ṇṭi</unclear> tulāsaṁkrāṁ<supplied reason="omitted">ti</supplied>nimityamuna ḍāka rēmi
